# $1 Base Collection Repository

Organizing a collection of repositories in a base folder.
The repositories can be updated using git submodules.

## Usage

### Status

```
git submodule foreach git status
```

### Pull Changes

```
git submodule foreach git pull --rebase --autostash origin <branch_name>
```

### Checkout

```
git submodule foreach git checkout dev
```

### Adding

```
git submodule add <repo_url>
```

## Reference

- https://dev.to/rmpato/a-new-use-case-for-git-submodules-3do1
- https://magit.vc/manual/magit/Submodule-Transient.html#Submodule-Transient